=== Uninstall ===

If you want to remove it. On Whonix-Workstation.

<pre>
sudo apt-get remove torchat
</pre>

And undo the changes in {{Code2|/etc/tor/torrc}} on Whonix-Gateway.

<pre>
nano /etc/tor/torrc
</pre>

Reload Tor.

<pre>
sudo service tor reload
</pre>

